p towards securing a job in the above sectors. It will be essential reading for those who want to forge a successful career in any area of the Criminal Justice Sector"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 0aCriminal justice, Administration of. 0aCareer development.1 aRees, Anne,eauthor.  aHV 7419 R346 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035223054  aHV 7419 R346 2015wLCc1i0162035223054lON_SHELFmUAAUGp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu1/14/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no96014330